This product includes components and patterns that were ported from, or
inspired by, the following open-source and reference projects. Their authors
are gratefully acknowledged:

- react-bits (https://github.com/DavidHDev/react-bits) — MIT License.
  The four-variant architecture (JS+CSS / JS+Tailwind / TS+CSS / TS+Tailwind)
  and several component implementations are derived from this project.

- designspells.com (https://www.designspells.com) — used as interaction-design
  reference for a number of micro-interactions. No code was copied; these
  components are independent reimplementations inspired by the documented
  interactions.

- reactbits.dev (https://reactbits.dev) — additional component reference.

Each component's source of inspiration is recorded in its entry in
apps/website/src/constants/Information.js.
